  <description><![CDATA[<p>This elegant hotel has been a focal point of Cervinia for many years. The Zanetti family have owned the Excelsior Planet for the past few decades and have created a haven to return to after a day’s skiing. The newly designed cocktail bar, restaurant and lounge with its roaring fireplace create a welcoming and sophisticated feel. The hotel prides itself on its delicious Italian cuisine that is beautifully prepared by an exceptional team of chefs.</p>]]></description>
